{"title":"vite配置https","uid":"55764d82013bf7d28ae08f515ae0da0c","slug":"Vite配置https证书/index","date":"2022-10-21T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-04-07T04:05:04.201Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Vite配置https证书/index.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h3 id=\"1-全局安装mkcert\"><a href=\"#1-全局安装mkcert\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.全局安装mkcert\"></a>1.全局安装<code>mkcert</code></h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cmd\" data-language=\"cmd\"><code class=\"language-cmd\">$ npm i mkcert -g</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"2-在任意目录，打开终端输入指令，生成ca证书\"><a href=\"#2-在任意目录，打开终端输入指令，生成ca证书\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.在任意目录，打开终端输入指令，生成ca证书\"></a>2.在任意目录，打开终端输入指令，生成ca证书</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cmd\" data-language=\"cmd\"><code class=\"language-cmd\">$ mkcert create-ca</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"3-再根据ca证书生成cert证书\"><a href=\"#3-再根据ca证书生成cert证书\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.再根据ca证书生成cert证书\"></a>3.再根据ca证书生成cert证书</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cmd\" data-language=\"cmd\"><code class=\"language-cmd\">$ mkcert create-cert localhost 127.0.0.1</code></pre>\n\n<p>双击<code>ca.crt</code>导入证书</p>\n<p>点击 安装证书—&gt;勾选本地计算机—&gt;选择将所有证书都放入下列存储中的受信任的根证书颁发机构—&gt;确定<br>导入成功<br>将cert.crt和cert.key放到项目的src&#x2F;assets&#x2F;ssl目录下</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-配置证书\"><a href=\"#4-配置证书\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.配置证书\"></a>4.配置证书</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">export default defineConfig(&#123;\n  plugins: [vue()],\n  server: &#123;\n    host: &#39;0.0.0.0&#39;,\n    https: &#123;\n      cert: fs.readFileSync(path.join(__dirname, &#39;src&#x2F;assets&#x2F;ssl&#x2F;cert.crt&#39;)),\n      key: fs.readFileSync(path.join(__dirname, &#39;src&#x2F;assets&#x2F;ssl&#x2F;cert.key&#39;))\n    &#125;\n  &#125;,\n&#125;)</code></pre>","text":"1.全局安装mkcert$ npm i mkcert -g 2.在任意目录，打开终端输入指令，生成ca证书$ mkcert create-ca 3.再根据ca证书生成cert证书$ mkcert create-cert localhost 127.0.0.1 双击ca.crt导入...","link":"","photos"